Hello! This documentation is supposed to tell you all your system requirements to run this game as well as any error or bugs you many encounter (to our knowledge)! In order to run Phantom of Visteria, you must have Godot 4 downloaded. To Download, visit https://godotengine.org/download/windows/

Hardware Minimum Requirements:

Operating System:
Windows: At least Windows 7
MacOS: 10.13 or 10.15
Linux: Any model after 2016

Graphics Card:
Forward+ rendering method: Integrated graphics with full Vulkan 1.0 support
Mobile rendering method: Integrated graphics with full Vulkan 1.0 support
Compatibility rendering method: Integrated graphics with full OpenGL 3.3 support

Random Access Memory (RAM):
Minimum: 4GB
Recommended: 8 GB

Storage:
At least 200 MB for Godot
At least 375 MB to run Phantom of Visteria

Common Errors:

Project not Loading:
Godot is slow in rendering this project, please wait a moment when loading the game
If the game does not load, try to exit out and re-import it

